data.description:
Rare, newer (1978) single story 1,263 sf home on a large corner lot with concrete pad & covered RV parking space. This is one of 25 homes in Maison Estates and has upgraded features including; Granite tile kitchen counter tops, Stainless appliances, Plantation style shutters, Sunroom, Low maintenance front
and backyards, Living room fireplace, Large corner lot and more.  This home is located in one of Hemet's newer 55+ neighborhoods,  which is close to the clubhouse, banquet room, community pool & Spa.
data.whatILove: Is in a large corner spot ,with a mazing natural light around the house,very quiet area,close to super Walmart and shopping centers.
